articles.author: Maxwell Zeff
articles.title: Google unveils a next-gen AI reasoning model - TechCrunch
articles.description: Google has unveiled Gemini 2.5, the company's new family of AI reasoning models that will pause to 'think' before answering.
articles.content:
On Tuesday, Google unveiled Gemini 2.5, a new family of AI reasoning models that pauses to “think” before answering a question.
